titles.title: To extend the duty suspension on S-Y(5-Methoxy-2-oxo-1,3,4-thiadiazol-3(2H)-yl)methyl?- O,O-dimethyl phosphorodithioate.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary:
12/18/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the duty suspension on S-Y(5-Methoxy-2-oxo-1,3,4-thiadiazol-3(2H)-yl)methyl?- O,O-dimethyl phosphorodithioate.
